At the end of the accounts for the examples, we must not go too far.
In February of this year we informed you of the arrival of the virtual operator Mobilking in Poland.
In just half a year, this operator has managed to conquer over 100 thousand customers and become the fifth largest local operator.
At the same time behind Mobilking is the Penta financial group to which in the Czech Republic belongs between the other U:fon.
The advantage of virtual operators is the possibility of focusing on a much more concrete Bersaille group.
